  <!-- Boomalope - Muffalo -->
  <ThingDef ParentName="AnimalThingBase" ADogSaidBody="Legs">
    <defName>Boomffalo</defName>
    <label>boomffalo</label>
    <description>A Boomalope / Muffalo hybrid. A bit unstable to transport goods, so it isn't ever used as a pack animal, but it produces milk and wool. From a genetic engineering standpoint, these creatures are hard to stabilize, since the muffalo's biology is incompatible with the boomalope's chemical sacs. A cocktail of chemical refrigerants is used to maintain a delicate balance.\n\nUseful abilities: Produces low quality milk and average wool. Explodes with Frostbite damage on death.</description>
    <statBases>
      <MoveSpeed>3.15</MoveSpeed>
      <ComfyTemperatureMin>-45</ComfyTemperatureMin>
